---
// The Space's Overview folded into Home (`/`, SpaceHomeView) — web-space-home-dashboard.
// This route now just redirects so old bookmarks / handoff links don't 404. The
// setup/edit flow still lives at /integrations/configure (a focused sub-flow reached
// from Home); the post-Configure confirmation lands on /?status=running|saved.
// Query string is preserved so any in-flight ?status= carries through to Home.
return Astro.redirect(`/${Astro.url.search}`, 302);
